<p><strong>Reading left to right, the steps get taller: 1, 2, 3, 4, 5, 6, 7.</strong></p>
<p><strong>How many steps are there? Circle one:</strong> 5 · 7 · 9</p>
<p><strong>Which step is the tallest? Circle one:</strong> the first (front) · the last (back)</p>
<p>Record <strong>one video</strong> — one take, no stopping (a phone is fine). Show these in order:</p>
